text.tspan: How do key COVID-19 metrics compare to the early 2021 peak?, United
Each metric is shown as a percentage of its peak value in early 2021, and is shifted to account for the observed delay between
case confirmation, hospitalization, ventilation, and death.
Source: UK Government COVID-19 Dashboard – Last updated 12 March 2023
